{"tid":2041984,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"朱克伯格：密切留意港局勢　冀續提供 FB 及 Whatsapp 服務","createTime":"2020-05-29T14:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T17:49:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c99ff6bbb2fda19af385d59eeab3aa6ccd78b9","tid":2041984,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200529-20_E2S7e_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200529-20_E2S7e_1200x0.png&h=9f6144c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook 行政總裁朱克伯格 (Mark Zuckerberg) 今日接受《霍士新聞》訪問時談及香港情況，指香港市民普遍喜歡使用 FB，與世界各地的親友保持聯繫，亦喜愛Whatsapp的加密技術，因此會密切關意香港局勢發展，在實施「港版國安法」後，希望 FB 可以找到方法，繼續為香港提供 FB 及 Whatsapp 服務。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，中美正就控制互聯網在全球打「思想戰」(battle of ideas)，認為在其他國家很常見，不少國家正嘗試弄清互聯網價值和規則。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國及北韓是無法使用FB，朱克伯格指有關地方未能提供服務，原因涉及「甚為壓迫的政策」(pretty oppressive policies)，有別於歐美等其他地方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國安法壓港-朱克伯格-密切留意港局勢-冀續提供-fb-及-whatsapp-服務/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC-%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-%E5%86%80%E7%BA%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B-fb-%E5%8F%8A-whatsapp-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33E9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=17148c16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC-%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-%E5%86%80%E7%BA%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B-fb-%E5%8F%8A-whatsapp-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%2F&h=639e2cee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國安法壓港-朱克伯格-密切留意港局勢-冀續提供-fb-及-whatsapp-服務/</a>"},{"pid":"1643e000db5cbb2467c98355dc4a30ab10e15a84","tid":2041984,